  "text": "The Service-Oriented Context Aware Middleware (SOCAM) [CITATION_1] , Context-Awareness Sub-Structure (CASS) [CITATION_2] , and Context Managing Frameworks are centralized architectures that in general receive context data from distributed context sensor and offer it in mostly processed to the clients.",
